# Active Directory Management

## Overview

This phase of the project focused on organizing Active Directory to better simulate a real-world enterprise environment. Organizational Units (OUs), security groups, user accounts, and workstation objects were organized to support future onboarding, offboarding, permissions management, and help desk ticket workflows.

---

## Create WoodTech Organizational Unit (OU)

- Log into `CA-DC-01`
- Open:
  - Server Manager
  - Tools
  - Active Directory Users and Computers
- Right click the domain
- Select:
  - New
  - Organizational Unit
- Create:
  - WoodTech

