## Create Help Desk Administrator Account

Navigate to:

```text
WoodTech > IT
```

Create a new user:

| Field | Value |
|---------|---------|
| First Name | HelpDesk |
| Last Name | Admin |
| Username | helpdesk.admin |

Password Configuration:

- Set password
- Uncheck:
  - User must change password at next logon
- Check:
  - Password never expires

Purpose:

- Dedicated technician account
- Used to manage tickets
- Used for user administration tasks
- Used for troubleshooting activities

